{"tid":918244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲格有意接手教拜仁","createTime":"2018-11-27T05:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T06:44:40.000Z","uid":31314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"45311427c28350cd32c5cf650cdcafd430222a9b","tid":918244,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:09:22.000Z","msg":"雲格離開阿仙奴之後一直未有新工作，早前富咸找他出山卻被拒絕，但現在拜仁出手情況可能不同。<br />\n<br />\n由於尼高高華今季領軍在德甲表現反覆，他們很想找雲格上任，而這位法國籍名帥已經有意重執教鞭。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=WdnXGFwYqTUALziYLj88rp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8a822960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n帶領拜仁大炒阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/6c/23/64/6c23642a3ed714c973cf878c32b88563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F6c%2F23%2F64%2F6c23642a3ed714c973cf878c32b88563.jpg&h=61179f69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5475d76ff3061ff5fc16957593d1015ff16c8610","tid":918244,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24f490f7f6e55be9de6d901e6aaf473f4f2e44b","tid":918244,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"真係落歐霸狙擊阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf88ce4fdac8ffca1fb349fc04dcb4b2b4f120a","tid":918244,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"叛徒"},{"pid":"a8e22ad027af03931ac52f47d1157b80ea8a799d","tid":918244,"uid":41524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc